<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
       <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="og:description" content="Interested in Listing your Service or Discord Community on our website? Fill out this application to apply for partner" />
    <meta name="og:image" content="https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/630858840585535498/750450513304223885/image0.png" />
    <meta name="og:title" content="Paradise Bot List | Partner Application" />
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#758acf" />
    <meta name="keywords" content="discordbots.org , top.gg, Discordbots.co , Bots , bot list , paradisebots.net, discord bot list , discord boats , blaze , lists, discord bots , discord bots list">
    <meta property="og:description" content="Interested in Listing your Service or Discord Community on our website? Fill out this application to apply for partner" />
    <meta name="og:image" content="https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/630858840585535498/750450513304223885/image0.png" />
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#758acf" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://www.w3schools.com/w3css/4/w3.css">
  <link rel="shortcut icon" href="https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/630858840585535498/750450513304223885/image0.png" style="border-radius: 80px;" type="image/x-icon">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">
  <title>Paradise Bot List | Partner Application</title>
</head>

<style>
* {
  box-sizing: border-box;
}
body {
  font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
}
/* Float four columns side by side */
.column {
  float: center;
  width: 25%;
  padding: 0 10px;
}
/* Remove extra left and right margins, due to padding */
.row {margin: 0 -5px;}
/* Clear floats after the columns */
.row:after {
  content: "";
  display: table;
  clear: both;
}
/* Responsive columns */
@media screen and (max-width: 600px) {
  .column {
    width: 100%;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
}
/* Style the counter cards */
.partner_apps_card {
  border-radius: 10px;
  box-shadow: 1px 1px 25px #888888;
  width: 75%;
  height: 75%;
  padding: 20px 10px;
  background-color: rgb(117, 138, 207);
  color: rgb(117, 138, 207);
  animation: fadeIn 1s;
  text-align: left;
}
.alert {
  padding: 20px;
  background-color: #f44336;
  color: white;
}
</style>

<body>
<%- include("../partials/header", { bot, user, path, }) %>
<br>
<center>
    <% if (alert) { %>
      <div style="background-color: rgb(151, 255, 177);  border: solid; border-color: black; width: 100%; height: 40px; border-radius: 20px; padding: 6px">
        <b style="color: rgb(70, 150, 70);"><%= alert %></b>
      </div>
    <% }else if(error){ %>
      <div style="background-color: rgb(255, 87, 87);  border: solid; border-color: black; width: 100%; height: 40px; border-radius: 20px; padding: 6px">
        <b style="color: white;"><%= error %></b>
      </div>
      <% } %>
    </center>
      <br>
<center>
        <h1>Partner Applications</h1>
        <div class="partner_apps_card">
        <p>Interested in Partnering with us? Fill out the application below</p>
          <p>• Please make sure you meet the requirements found on our <a href="https://docs.paradisebots.net/internal/community/partnership/">docs</a></p>
          <p>• If you need help with this Application please feel free to ask for assistance in our <a href="https://paradisebots.net/join/">Discord Server</a></p>
        <hr>
<form method="post">
<p style="color: white;"><i class="fa fa-fw fa-info-circle"></i> Why and What do you want to partner?:<br></p>
<textarea class="input" style="width: 75%; height: 150px;" name="reason_for_partner" placeholder="Give us some details here on why you want to partner and what kind of service you want to partner (ie: Discord Server)" required></textarea>
<hr>
<p style="color: white;"><i class="fa fa-fw fa-info-circle"></i>Provide a link:<br></p>
<p> • Link to your Website, Server ETC</p>
<input name="invite" style="width: 75%; height: 50px;" class="input" placeholder="dicord.gg/pwuyox" required>
<hr>
<p style="color: white;"><i class="fa fa-fw fa-info-circle" ></i>What are you Partnering?:<br></p>
<select name="what_youre_partnering" required>
  <option value="Discord Server">Server</option>
  <option value="Business/Website">Business/Website</option>
  <option value="Discord Bot">Discord Bot</option>
</select>
<hr>
<p style="color: white;"><i class="fa fa-fw fa-info-circle" ></i>Server member count (Excluding bots):<br></p>
<p> • Select "None" if you are not partnering a Server</p>
<select name="members" required>
  <option value="None" required>None</option>
  <option value="< 100">< 100</option>
  <option value="100">100 + </option>
  <option value="200">200 +</option>
  <option value="300">300 +</option>
  <option value="400">400 +</option>
  <option value="500">500 +</option>
</select>
<hr>
<p style="color: white;"><i style="color: white;" class="fa fa-fw fa-info-circle"></i> What can you offer?:<br></p>
<textarea style="width: 75%; height: 150px;" class="input" name="what_you_offer" placeholder="Tell us why we should pick you (advantages)" required>
</textarea>
<hr>
<input type="checkbox" style="color: white;" name="agreement" value="Agree" required>
<b style="color: white;"><label for="agreement"> By applying for the PBL Partnership Program i hereby agree to be bound by the <a href="https://docs.paradisebots.net/internal/community/partnership/">Requirements</a> & <a href="https://paradisebots.net/terms">Terms of Service</a></label></b>
<hr>
<button class="button" name="submit" style="width: 170px;" value="Submit partner program">Send App</button>
</form>
</div>
</center>
<br><br>
<%- include("../partials/footer") %>
</body> 
</html>
